              <ul class="text-sm list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-content/70">
                <li>Group stories by entity ownership</li>
                <li>Apply business capability grouping within entity boundaries</li>
                <li>Keep contexts flat (no nested contexts)</li>
                <li>Identify components within each context</li>
                <li>Map dependencies between contexts</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

