                <li>Follow template structure (purpose, entities, access patterns, etc.)</li>
                <li>Be specific about behavior, edge cases, error handling</li>
                <li>Include acceptance criteria from relevant user stories</li>
                <li>List every component (file) that needs to be implemented</li>
